      <h2>1. When in doubt, always pick a classic</h2>
      <p>
        Every layered stack needs a proper foundation. This foundation is your comfort chain—the one you can wear alone any day.
        Choose a simple, minimal chain that sits closest to your neck. This sets the tone for the rest of the layers and provides
